omes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20strategic%20choice%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFebruary%202023%20marked%20the%20turning%20point.%20Ajay%20chose%20Anthropology%2C%20a%20subject%20that%20immediately%20appealed%20to%20him%20with%20its%20well-defined%2C%20concise%20syllabus%20and%20a%20personal%20fascination%20with%20tribal%20cultures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20change%20of%20subject%3B%20it%20was%20a%20step%20towards%20clarity%20and%20confidence.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20that%20mastering%20Anthropology%20could%20unlock%20the%20door%20to%20achieving%20the%20cut-off%20and%20beyond.%20It%20was%20the%20best%20choice%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20shares%20reasons%20that%20made%20Anthropology%20a%20strategic%20choice%20for%20him%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1)%20Defined%20syllabus%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20syllabus%20of%20Anthropology%20is%20well-defined%20and%20relatively%20concise%2C%20making%20it%20more%20manageable%20within%20the%20limited%20preparation%20time%20Ajay%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2)%20Predictability%20of%20questions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20questions%20in%20Anthropology%20papers%20are%20more%20predictable%2C%20with%20themes%20and%20questions%20often%20repeating%20over%20the%20years%2C%20allowing%20for%20targeted%20preparation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-2-1751458727.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ajay%20with%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-2-1751458727.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett