ugh%20each%20topic%20thoroughly%20to%20ensure%20he%20understood%20the%20breadth%20and%20depth%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2)%20Effective%20revision%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20revising%20at%20least%20twice%20between%20the%20prelims%20and%20mains.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307829%2Frevision-tips-for-upsc-cse-mains-optional-subject-by-ias-officer-akshita-gupta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrategic%20third%20revision%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20done%20right%20after%20finishing%20the%20General%20Studies%20papers%2C%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20five-day%20gap%20before%20the%20optional%20exams.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20timing%20was%20key%20to%20maintaining%20freshness%20in%20concepts%20and%20keeping%20them%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20my%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20year%2C%20Ajay%20successfully%20cleared%20the%20prestigious%20UPSC%20CSE%2C%20securing%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20705.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FAjay-IRS-upsc-cse-1-1751458735-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%