er%2080-100%20years%2C%20it%20ingeniously%20integrates%20farming%20and%20water%20management%20to%20conserve%20and%20use%20runoff%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20does%20this%20system%2C%20seemingly%20simple%20yet%20brilliantly%20executed%2C%20accomplish%20such%20feats%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20triple-tiered%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20Zabo%20refers%20specifically%20to%20a%20small%20pit%20within%20a%20paddy%20field%2C%20often%20used%20for%20fish%20rearing.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Ruza%20denotes%20a%20much%20larger%20pond%2C%20typically%20around%20point%20two%20hectares%20in%20size%2C%20designed%20to%20store%20run-off%20water%20from%20the%20upper%20slopes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ruza%20system%20is%20a%20triad%20of%20thriving%20forestry%20at%20hilltops%2C%20productive%20agriculture%20in%20the%20mid-section%2C%20and%20flourishing%20paddy%20fields%20below.%20The%20upper%20tier%20protects%20village%20forestland%2C%20maintaining%20biodiversity%20and%20water%20catchment.%20In%20the%20middle%20tier%2C%20the%20ponds%20and%20cattle%20yards%20synergise%20to%20nurture%20the%20fields%20below%2C%20which%20not%20only%20yield%20rice%20but%20also%20support%20fish%20rearing%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nutritious%20bonus%20that%20enriches%20the%20village%E2%80%99s%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(see%20figure)%20Schematic%20diagram%20of%20the%20Zabo%20farming%20system%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Schematic%20diagram%20of%20Zabo%20farming%20system.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXe1ucv8b2-al_vOzVWweS-dSux--5KbTS28XhsegzN1cVAE96PxTRMxThM400yLOCfcv41azq35p0kDiFY2dP_NXGQXK1Ka8buAFJOdwstqVbP24rGc8Wnh_YS7Ws7Uvy6TZ4sV%3Fkey%3DJro5jQ19UXkFaRzOGjeFhw%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESchematic%20diagram%20of%20the%20Zabo%20farming%20system.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Picture%