20electric%20models%20to%20choose%20from%20than%20those%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20they%20often%20don't%20need%20to%20break%20the%20bank%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20price%20of%20an%20EV%20in%20the%20US%20in%20May%20was%20around%20%2457%2C000%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coxautoinc.com%2Fmarket-insights%2Fev-market-monitor-may-2025%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Cox%20Automotive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20the%20%2432%2C000%20Nissan%20Leaf%20the%20cheapest%20model%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Seagull%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659533e7ab6f2ebb11f85d31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBYD's%20Seagull%20sells%20for%20less%20than%20%2410%2C000%20in%20China.%3Cp%3EWuYuan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20the%20average%20price%20of%20an%20electric%20car%20in%20China%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fbusiness%2Fchina-business%2Farticle%2F3293635%2Fchinese-ev-makers-cannot-stop-aggressive-price-cutting-even-it-imperils-them%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earound%20%2431%2C500%20as%20of%20December%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20best-selling%20models%20like%20the%20BYD%20Seagull%20selling%20for%20under%20%2410%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChinese%20and%20US%20EVs%20are%20currently%20in%20a%20very%20different%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Will%20Roberts%2C%20head%20of%20automotive%20research%20for%20battery%20and%20EV%20consultancy%20Rho%20Motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20has%20an%20incredibly%20broad%20range%20of%20EVs%20catering%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20entire%20market%2C%20while%20the%20development%20of%20EVs%20for%20many%20popular%20manufacturers%20in%20the%20US%20is%20still%20at%20a%20comparatively%20early%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20Roberts%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Western%20markets%20of