-year-of-efficiency-working-meta-ai-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg's%202023%20%26quot%3Byear%20of%20efficiency%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Tech%20companies%2C%20coming%20down%20from%20pandemic-era%20growth%2C%20began%20shifting%20toward%20leaner%20workforces.%20Now%2C%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20AI-driven%20productivity%20and%20rising%20global%20uncertainty%2C%20many%20organizations%20are%20doubling%20down%20on%20the%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Meta%20laid%20off%20some%204%2C000%20employees%20to%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternal-memo-meta-increases-employees-rated-below-expectations-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emove%20out%20low-performers%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20people%20on%20our%20teams.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20also%20cut%20nearly%202%2C000%20employees%2C%20whom%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eit%20said%20were%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ousted-employees-block-list-good-attrition-2025-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEarlier%2520this%2520year%252C%2520Microsoft%2520fired%2Cand%2520a%2520timeline%2520for%2520improvement.%2522%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderperformers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c81b057f-7bca-43c7-880f-a7fbda2722d4%5C%22%3EBut%20what's%20popular%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20can%20have%20mixed%20results%20in%20government%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20like%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20government%20trying%20to%20learn%20from%20successful%20private%20sector%20business%20processes%2C%20which%20I%20think%20could%20very%20frequently%20help%20the%20government%20do%20a%20better%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Steven%20J.%20Kelman%2C%20professor%20of%20public%20management%20at%20Harvard%20University's%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20School%20of%20Government%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Montgomery%20Van%20Wart%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20public%20administration%20at%20California%20State%20University%2C%20San%20Bernardino%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20compared%20to%20a%20company%20focused%20on%20profit%2C%20the%20public%20sector%20requires%20%26quot%3Bfar%20greater%26quot%3B%20transparency%2C%20accountability%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20procedural%20due%20process%2C%20which%20come%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20some%20degree%20of%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20trick%20for%20policymakers%20is%20to%20decide%20when%20public%20sector%20options%20are%20best%2C%20and%20when%20they%20need%20to%20change%20significantly%20and%20find%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Wart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227fff8444-b056-4e43-9c37-57450ec933b1%5C%22%3EA%20changing%20federal%20workforce%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20latest%20memo%20is%20part%20of%20a%20long%20string%20of%20changes%20made%20to%20the%20federal%20workforce%2C%20which%20employs%20over%203%20million%20people%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%20has%20adopted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-doge-work-silicon-vallery-grind-culture-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bhardcore%26quot%3B%20work%20attitude%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20X%20and%20Tesla%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenate-doge-cuts-rescission-package-npr-pbs-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%20DOGE%3C%2Fa%3E%20office's%20attempts%20to%20slim%20down%20the%20government%20and%20brought%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20approach%20to%20the%20federal%20government.%20Though%20the%20tech%20billionaire%20has%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-leaving-doge-reaction-white-house-trump-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeparted%20the%20White%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%20(and%20had%20a%20public%20falling%20out%20with%20Trump)%2C%20the%20ethos%20has%20remained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%2