h%20showed%20we're%20not%20alone%20in%20our%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40natattackz_%2Fphoto%2F7514149344451267886%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20people%20have%20questioned%20if%20there's%20an%20average%20or%20%26quot%3Bnormal%26quot%3B%20amount%20of%20cash%20everyone%20should%20gift%20at%20weddings%20these%20days.%20Others%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fwedding%2Fcomments%2F1gsq2i2%2Fhow_much_should_you_gift_a_couple_for_their%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReddit%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20asked%20where%20registry%20items%20enter%20the%20equation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20there's%20no%20clear%20winning%20answer%20among%20average%20internet%20users.%20Some%20commenters%20say%20%2450%20cash%20is%20sufficient%2C%20while%20others%20say%20your%20gift%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20in%20the%20form%20of%20money%20or%20a%20present%20%E2%80%94%20should%20cost%20no%20less%20than%20%24500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223657%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Table%20full%20of%20wedding%20gifts.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666ffcd6764df161125a474d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222422%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShould%20you%20give%20cash%2C%20a%20gift%2C%20or%20both%20to%20newlywed%20couples%3F%20No%20one%20really%20knows.%3Cp%3Enuiiko%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChelsea%20Fagan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20The%20Financial%20Diet%20and%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penguinrandomhouse.com%2Fbooks%2F768806%2Fhaving-people-over-by-chelsea-fagan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHaving%20People%20Over%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20uncertainty%20partially%20stems%20from%20the%20modern%20%26quot%3Binflation%20of%20the%20entire%20wedding%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhereas%20the%20average%20wedding%20was%20once%20small%2C%20local%2C%20and%20contained%20to%20a%20single%20day%2C%20it's%20now%20bigger%2C%20more%20luxurious%2C%20and%20comprised%20of%20multiple%20events%2C%20from%20multiday%20bachelor%20trips%20to%20welcome%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20really%20opening%20our%20pockets%20to%20an%20unsustainable%20degree%20for%20weddings%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20finance%20and%20etiquette%20writer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.creditkarma.com%2Fabout%2Fcommentary%2Fweddings-are-getting-smaller-farther-and-pricier-and-guests-feel-it-the-most%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECredit%20Karma%3C%2Fa%3E%20surveyed%201%2C106%20American%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%20and%20found%20that%2038%25%20took%20on%20debt%20to%20attend%20weddings%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20BI%20has%20also%20reported%20that%20some%20people%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-costs-bridesmaids-spend-bridal-party-no-resentment-worth-it-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espent%20over%20%2410%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20attend%20multiple%20ceremonies%20and%20receptions%20in%20less%20than%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGifts%20are%20only%20a%20small%20part%20of%20that%20equation%2C%20but%20they're%20expensive%20nonetheless.%20In%20an%20email%20to%20BI%2C%20Lauren%20Kay%2C%20the%20executive%20editor%20of%20The%20Knot%2C%20said%20a%202025%20study%20from%20the%20publication%20shows%20that%20the%20average%20wedding%20guest%20spends%20%24150%20on%20a%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296025ab7-4a18-4f0e-82b0-dbdb691f9d09%5C%22%3EBrides%20say%20they're%20getting%20the%20short%20end%20of%20the%20stick%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBowman%20Boone%20and%20her%20husband%20lived%20together%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years%20before%20getting%20married%2C%20so%20they%20didn't%20need%20to%20put%20an%20extensive%20registry%20together.%20Instead%2C%20they%20asked%20guests%20to%20contribute%20to%20a%20honeymoon%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20couple%20was%20thrilled%20to%20receive%20many%20cash%20and%20online%20deposits%2C%20Bowman%20Boone%20said%20their%20guests'%20efforts%20mattered%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20have%20people%20%5Bin%20different%20financial%20situations%5D%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20look%20at%20any%20of%20them%20differently%20if%20they%20didn't%20give%20us%20a%20financial%20or%20physical%20gift%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20everyone%20coming%20to%20my%20wedding%20was%20a%20gift%20in%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20everyone%20we%20invited%20to%20be%20there%20and%20celebrate%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wedding%20table%20with%20two%20chairs%20labeled%20%26quot%3BMr.%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BMrs.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68530afef748d8c055f3faa4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20the%20very%20least%2C%20some%20brides%20and%20grooms%20would%20like%20cards%20to%20signify%20their%20big%20days.%3Cp%3Ehsyncoban%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it%20stung%20when%20some%20family%20members%20and%20guests%20arrived%20without%20cards.%20Bowman%20Boone%20said%20it%20felt%20like%20her%20efforts%20as%20a%20host%20hadn't%20been%20reciprocated%2C%20and%20she%20couldn't%20understand%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrides%20on%20social%20media%20have%20expressed%20similar%20disappointments%20after%20their%20weddings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20had%20120%20people%20at%20our%20wedding%20and%20we%20only%20received%2012%20cards%20and%20four%20gifts%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40alizeruiz_%2Fvideo%2F7496170745731484970%3Fis_from_webapp%3D1%26sender_device%3Dpc%26web_id%3D7394903114639590955%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikToker%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20viral%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Ladouceur%20attends%20weddings%20for%20a%20living.%20She's%20a%20leader%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.planwithlaur.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edestination-wedding%20content%20creation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20involves%20attending%20weddings%20all%20over%20the%20world%20to%20capture%20high-quality%20iPhone%20content%20that%20couples%20can%20post%20on%20their%20social%20media%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20BI%20that%20no%20matter%20why%20some%20guests%20choose%20not%20to%20give%20gifts%2C%20it%20can%20still%20bother%20brides%20and%20grooms%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20even%20before%20their%20wedding%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20had%20couples%20come%20to%20me%20and%20say%2C%20'How%20do%20I%20get%20people%20to%20donate%20to%20my%20honeymoon%20fund%3F%20How%20do%20I%20get%20people%20to%20buy%20from%20my%20registry%3F%20Nothing's%20coming%20in%2C'%26quot%3B%20Ladouceur%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20we've%20moved%20away%20from%20tradition%2C%20which%20I%20ultimately%20think%20is%20a%20good%20thing%2C%20that%20transactional%20side%20to%20weddings%20is%20an%20unintended%20consequence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221b4482a-83d1-42f9-8de8-d390a73443bb%5C%22%3EThere's%20a%20solution%2C%20and%20both%20parties%20have%20a%20role%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20unsurprisingly%2C%20every%20person%20I%20spoke%20with%20felt%20differently%20about%20what%20to%20gift%2C%20when%20to%20present%20it%2C%20and%20how%20much%20to%20spend.%20However%2C%20there%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20few%20general%20rules%20of%20thumb%20that%20would%20be%20helpful%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFagan%20said%20couples%20getting%20married%20should%20stay%20%26quot%3Bconscientious%20about%20what%20they're%20asking%20of%20people%26quot%3B%20and%20consider%20how%20expensive%20weddings%20are%20to%20attend%2C%20especially%20if%20a%20guest%20is%20in%20their%20bridal%20party%20or%20attending%20other%20weddings%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20every%20right%20to%20ask%20for%20everything%20you%20want%2C%20but%20your%20guests%20also%20have%20a%20right%20to%20say%20no%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20wedding%20guests%2C%20give%20what%20you%20can%20and%20don't%20worry%20about%20following%20popular%20societal%20rules%2C%20like%20matching%20the%20cost%20of%20your%20food%20at%20a%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20%24150%20is%20not%20covering%20your%20plate%2C%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20weddings%20cost%20in%20any%20high-cost-of-living%20city%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20most%20cities%20these%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Ladouceur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFagan%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BFor%20every%20aspect%20of%20wedding%20attendance%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20very%20candid%20about%20what%20you%20can%20and%20can't%20do%2C%20and%20not%20feel%20guilty%20for%20setting%20reasonable%20boundaries%20around%20your%20finances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20traveling%20to%20attend%20a%20wedding%2C%20she%20said%20it's%20sufficient%20to%20hand-make%20a%20gift%20or%20simply%20give%20a%20card%20%E2%80%94%20so%20long%20as%20your%20care%20and%20efforts%20are%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20couples%20ultimately%20want%2C%20Ladouceur%20said%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bto%20know%20you're%20excited%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20less%20that%20people%20remember%20what%20gift%20you%20gave%2C%20and%20more%20that%20they%20remember%20how%20you%20showed%20up%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-gift-amount-confusing-guests-bride-groom-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751452321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6855c339f748d8c055f41891%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessins