ss%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20wastelands%20to%20farmlands%3A%20How%20one%20scientist%20sparked%20a%20powerful%20green%20revolution%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20began%20as%20a%20simple%20assignment%20soon%20became%20a%20life%E2%80%99s%20mission%20for%20%3Cstrong%3EDr%20Lal%20Singh%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20When%20he%20first%20joined%20%3Cstrong%3ECSIR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%202013%2C%20he%20was%20only%20trying%20to%20prove%20himself%20to%20his%20seniors.%20But%20what%20followed%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20his%20career%E2%80%94and%20the%20lives%20of%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20assigned%20to%20convert%20a%20uranium%20tailing%20pond%20in%20Jharkhand%20back%20in%202006.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20joined%20CSIR.%20We%20adopted%20the%20bamboo%20plantation%20method%20to%20eradicate%20the%20water%20and%20land%20pollution%20in%20the%20site%2C%20and%20it%20worked.%20This%20was%20my%20first%20project%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20looking%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESingh%20shares%20with%20The%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20this%20first%20attempt%20planted%20a%20seed%20in%20him%E2%80%94if%20a%20dead%2C%20polluted%20pond%20could%20be%20revived%2C%20what%20else%20could%20be%20brought%20back%20to%20life%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-07-01-at-10.15.04-2_2_11zon-1751348891.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eco-Rejuvenation%20Technology%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-07-01-at-10.15.04-2_2_11zon-1751348891.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-07-01-at-10.15.04-2_2_11zon-1751348891-300x135.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-07-01-at-10.15.04-2_2_11zon-1751348891-500x225.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-07-01-at-10.15.04-2_2_11zon-1751348891-768x346.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-07-01-at-10.15.04-2_2_11zon-1751348891-1536x691.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-07-01-at-10.15.04-2_2_11zon-1751348891-150x68.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458844%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStep%20by%20step%2C%20project%20by%20project%2C%20Dr%20Singh%20and%20his%20team%20proved%20that%20barren%2C%20damaged%20lands%20could%20be%20saved.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20Dr%20Singh%20faced%20a%20bigger%20challenge.%20He%20was%20asked%20to%20convert%20degraded%2C%20fly%20ash-laden%20land%20near%20Nagpur%20in%20Maharashtra%20into%20something%20useful%20for%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20my%20first%20project%20in%20the%20state.%20I%20was%20given%20Ubagi%20and%20Khapari%20villages%20in%20Maharashtra.%20They%20are%2024%20kms%20away%20from%20Nagpur.%20I%20worked%20on%20a%2010-hectare%20polluted%20wasteland%20and%20in%20two%20years%20it%20was%20rejuvenated%20and%20in%20four%20years%20it%20was%20ready%20for%20crop%20cultivation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%20by%20step%2C%20project%20by%20project%2C%20Dr%20Singh%20and%20his%20team%20proved%20that%20barren%2C%20damaged%20lands%20could%20be%20saved.%20This%20was%20no%20quick%20fix%E2%80%94it%20took%20years%20of%20planting%2C%20soil%20care%2C%20and%20patient%20observation.%20But%20each%20patch%20of%20green%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20local%20farmers%20to%20return%2C%20grow%20food%2C%20and%20build%20healthier%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20technical%20experiment%20has%20quietly%20grown%20into%20a%20movement%E2%80%94a%20green%20revolution%20that%20not%20only%20cleans%20the%20land%20but%20also%20restores%20livelihoods.%20For%20Dr%20Singh%2C%20this%20work%20is%20no%20longer%20just%20a%20job.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20mission%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20polluted%2C%20forgotten%20places%20can%20be%20turned%20into%20homes%20for%20trees%2C%20crops%2C%20and%20people%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFly%20ash%2C%20forgotten%20lands%2C%20and%20the%20villages%20that%20paid%20the%20price%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20the%20villages%20near%20the%20thermal%20power%20plants%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Vidarbha%20district%20lived%20under%20a%20cloud%E2%80%94quite%20literally.%20Fly%20ash%20from%20the%20power%20plants%20settled%20on%20their%20crops%2C%20filled%20their%20air%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329441%2Fchennai-startup-bookwater-tracks-water-cans-quality-with-qr-codes-helps-access-safe-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolluted%20their%20water%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20land%2C%20once%20rich%20and%20alive%2C%20slowly%20turned%20into%20a%20dumping%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20seven%20years%20since%20the%20people%20belonging%20to%20adjacent%20villages%20forgot%20about%20the%20fly%20ash%20problem%2C%20the%20air%2C%20soil%2C%20and%20water%20pollution%20it%20caused.%20All%20thanks%20to%20the%20eco%20rejuvenation%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3Cstrong%3EDr%20Lal%20Singh%20in%20conversation%20with%20the%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFly%20ash%2C%20a%20fine%20powdery%20waste%20released%20from%20burning%20coal%2C%20was%20dumped%20into%20low-lying%20areas%20near%20the%20power%20plants.%20These%20tailing%20ponds%20became%20large%20pits%20of%20toxic%20waste.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20ash%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20stay%20in%20the%20ponds%E2%80%94it%20blew%20over%20the%20fields%2C%20settled%20on%20crops%2C%20mixed%20into%20the%20water%2C%20and%20filled%20the%20air%20people%20breathed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20the%20fly%20ash%20problem%2C%20farmers%E2%80%99%20productivity%20was%20reduced%20drastically%20as%20the%20fly%20ash%20settled%20on%20their%20crops.%20Women%20had%20no%20livelihood%2C%20and%20everyone%20in%20the%20nearby%20villages%20breathed%20bad%20air.%20The%20team%20decided%20to%20eradicate%20all%20the%20problems%20and%20began%20to%20rejuvenate%20dump%20sites%2C%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Lal%20Singh%20explains%2C%20his%20voice%20carrying%20the%20weight%20of%20what%20these%20villages%20had%20suffered.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20damage%20was%20not%20just%20to%20the%20land%E2%80%94it%20affected%20entire%20communities.%20Crops%20failed%2C%20incomes%20dried%20up%2C%20and%20clean%20air%20became%20a%20luxury.%20But%20turning%20things%20around%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClearing%20the%20lands%20for%20bamboo%20cultivation%20was%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20of%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Singh%20shares.%20The%20soil%20was%20weak%2C%20the%20waste%20was%20thick%2C%20and%20preparing%20the%20ground%20for%20new%20life%20demanded%20relentless%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20despite%20these%20obstacles%2C%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Dr%20Singh%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20his%20team%20pushed%20forward%E2%80%94step%20by%20step%2C%20tree%20by%20tree%E2%80%94showing%20that%20even%20the%20most%20forgotten%20lands%20could%20be%20brought%20back%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20rejuvenated%20lands%20brought%20new%20life%20to%20farmers%20and%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20farmers%20in%20these%20villages%20struggled%20to%20grow%20their%20crops.%20The%20fly%20ash%20from%20nearby%20power%20plants%20settled%20on%20their%20fields%2C%20coating%20%3Cstrong%3Epulses%2C%20cotton%2C%20and%20soya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20with%20a%20fine%20layer%20of%20dust.%20Their%20harvests%20shrank%2C%20their%20incomes%20disappeared%2C%20and%20their%20hope%20slowly%20faded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSlide1_1_11zon-1751348883.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eco-Rejuvenation%20Technology%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSlide1_1_11zon-1751348883.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSlide1_1_11zon-1751348883-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSlide1_1_11zon-1751348883-500x225.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSlide1_1_11zon-1751348883-768x346.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSlide1_1_11zon-1751348883-1536x691.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSlide1_1_11zon-1751348883-150x68.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20years%2C%20people%20believed%20these%20areas%20around%20Koradi%2C%20Khaparkheda%2C%20and%20Chandrapur%20Thermal%20Power%20Stations%20were%20beyond%20saving.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fly%20ash%20has%20a%20component%20called%20%E2%80%98silica%E2%80%99%20which%20usually%20settles%20on%20the%20crops.%20This%20cut%20down%20the%20productivity%20of%20the%20crops.%20Bamboo%20is%20a%20plant%20that%20attracts%20silica%2C%20and%20this%20helps%20in%20making%20sure%20crops%20are%20not%20affected%20as%20the%20bamboo%20sites%20attract%20most%20of%20the%20silica%20in%20the%20air%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cstrong%3Eexplains%20Dr%20Lal%20Singh%2C%20sharing%20the%20simple%20but%20powerful%20science%20behind%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20planting%20bamboo%2C%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20just%20adding%20greenery%E2%80%94they%20were%20creating%20a%20natural%20shield%2C%20a%20silent%20protector%20that%20would%20pull%20silica%20out%20of%20the%20air%20and%20away%20from%20the%20crops.%20Slowly%2C%20the%20air%20grew%20cleaner%2C%20the%20soil%20stronger%2C%20and%20the%20village%20lives%20began%20to%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20seven%20years%20since%20we%20have%20had%20this%20green%20belt%20and%20we%20are%20fortunate%20to%20breathe%20clean%20air%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3Cstrong%3EPranali%20Sahara%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20%3Cstrong%3EKoradi%20Nahadula%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20village%20just%2010%20km%20from%20the%20dump%20site.%20Pranali%2C%20a%20single%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20never%20imagined%20this%20dead%20land%20could%20become%20a%20place%20of%20work%20and%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20worked%20here%20for%20the%20last%20seven%20years.%20We%20never%20thought%20this%20place%20would%20transform%20like%20this.%20Today%20we%20have%20clean%20air%2C%20water%2C%20and%20healthy%20soil.%20I%20am%20the%20only%20one%20who%20earns%20in%20my%20family%2C%20and%20I%20also%20got%20a%20job%20because%20of%20this%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cstrong%3Eshe%20shares%20with%20a%20smile%20that%20carries%20both%20gratitude%20and%20quiet%20strength.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Pranali%20now%20earns%20%3Cstrong%3ERs%205000%20a%20month%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20tending%20to%20the%20bamboo%20plantation%2C%20caring%20for%20the%20site%20that%20has%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20cared%20for%20her%20in%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20cleaning%20the%20land%20to%20watering%20the%20bamboo%20trees%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20site%2C%20we%20have%2020%20women%20employed.%20All%20these%20women%20are%20employed%20on%20a%20three-year%20contract.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-23_11zon-1751358635.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Eco-Rejuvenation%20Technology%20is%20an%20eco-friendly%2C%20cost-effective%20solution%20developed%20by%20CSIR-NEERI%20(Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20%E2%80%93%20National%20Environmental%20Engineering%20Research%20Institute).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-23_11zon-1751358635.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-23_11zon-1751358635-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-23_11zon-1751358635-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-23_11zon-1751358635-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-23_11zon-1751358635-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-459050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Eco-Rejuvenation%20Technology%20is%20an%20eco-friendly%2C%20cost-effective%20solution%20developed%20by%20CSIR-NEERI%20(Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20%E2%80%93%20National%20Environmental%20Engineering%20Research%20Institute).%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20them%20is%20%3Cstrong%3EGeeta%20Chauhan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20another%20mother%20from%20the%20same%20village.%20With%20two%20children%20depending%20on%20her%2C%20Geeta%20says%20the%20opportunity%20came%20when%20she%20needed%20it%20most.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20six%20years%20since%20I%20have%20worked%20at%20the%20site%