0contaminated%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20selecting%20the%20bamboo%20sapling%20is%20a%20crucial%20process%2C%20Dr%20Singh%20says%20that%20picking%20a%20species%20of%20bamboo%20that%20consumes%20less%20water%20is%20important%2C%20as%20most%20parts%20of%20Maharashtra%20face%20water%20scarcity.%20%E2%80%9CI%20usually%20select%20a%20plant%20that%20is%20cost-friendly%20and%20has%20a%20high%20leaf%20persistence%20value.%20A%20leaf%20with%20a%20high%20leaf%20persistence%20value%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20wither%20away%20easily.%20The%20sapling%20should%20also%20be%20fast-growing%20and%20mitigate%20dust%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20scientist%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20green%20revolution%20beyond%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20breathing%20life%20back%20into%20the%20dusty%20lands%20of%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Vidarbha%20region%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EDr%20Lal%20Singh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20his%20team%20are%20not%20stopping.%20The%20success%20here%20has%20become%20a%20starting%20point%E2%80%94a%20blueprint%20for%20healing%20broken%20lands%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20next%20mission%20takes%20them%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EOdisha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20where%20the%20land%20tells%20a%20different%20story%20of%20damage.%20%E2%80%9CA%20site%20in%20Odisha%2C%20which%20is%20polluted%20because%20of%20phosphorus%20ore%2C%20is%20our%20next%20target.%20We%20plan%20to%20implement%20ERT%20with%20bamboo%20saplings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Singh%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-25_11zon-2-1751358741.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Their%20next%20mission%20takes%20them%20to%20Odisha%2C%20where%20the%20land%20tells%20a%20different%20story%20of%20damage.%5C%2