%2Fdoctors-day-1-1751290140-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fdoctors-day-1-1751290140-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458463%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20Dr%20Rahman%2C%20medicine%20transcends%20the%20commercial%20gain%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%2C%20above%20all%2C%20a%20sacred%20duty.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dr%20Rahman%2C%20work%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20with%20the%20setting%20sun.%20Nights%20often%20find%20him%20attending%20to%20emergencies%2C%20sleeping%20only%20after%20ensuring%20patients%E2%80%99%20stability.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20operate%20between%2011%20am%20and%2011%20pm.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20need%20to%20extend%20working%20hours%2C%20too.%20Just%20last%20night%2Ctwo%20heart%20attack%20patients%20came%20in.%20I%20came%20back%20home%20after%20midnight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20he%20finds%20balance.%20%E2%80%9CI%20sleep%20soundly%20during%20non-working%20hours.%20This%20allows%20me%20to%20function%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20Dr%20Rahman%20says%2C%20has%20been%20his%20lifestyle%20for%20the%20past%2015%20years.%20Over%20these%20years%2C%20Dr%20Rahman%E2%80%99s%20impact%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20thousands%20of%20patients%20he%20has%20treated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20blessing%20during%20the%20darkest%20days%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20patients%2C%20Hamza%20Khaild%2C%20recalls%20how%20Dr%20Rahman%E2%80%99s%20kindness%20saved%20his%20family%20from%20financial%20ruin.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202022%2C%20my%20father%20had%20a%20paralytic%20stroke%20during%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20We%20admitted%20him%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Begusarai%2C%20but%20in%20one%20week%2C%20the%20bill%20touched%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20We%20were%20devastated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%2C%20we%20cons